Package com.capgemini.cobigen.impl.config.entity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMatcher
    Common declaration of all available matcher types
    ContainerMatcher
    The ContainerMatcher type corresponds to the <containerMatcher> xml node
    Increment
    Storage class for increments provided within the config.xml
    Matcher
    The Matcher type corresponds to the <matcher> xml node
    Template
    Storage class for template data provided within the config.xml
    TemplateFile
    Virtual file system for generation target to evaluate path variables and cobigen specific symlinks.
    TemplateFolder
    Virtual file system for generation target to evaluate path variables and cobigen specific symlinks.
    TemplatePath
    Interface as abstraction for a Path in a TemplateFolder.
    Trigger
    Storage class for trigger data provided within the context.xml
    VariableAssignment
    A VariableAssignment key value pair, which will be interpreted by any plug-in declaring the VariableAssignment.type
    Variables
    This class is a container for variables that can inherit from parent Variables building a hierarchy.
